        <div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-6 col-md-4"> 
        <div class="panel panel-default">
  						<div class="panel-heading">
    						<h3 class="panel-title">NSB Activities</h3>
  						</div>
 					<div class="panel-body">
        
                <p>The NSB establishes the policies of  the National Science Foundation and serves as advisor to Congress and the  President. The Board approves major NSF awards, provides congressional  testimony and issues statements relevant to the nation&rsquo;s S&amp;E enterprise.</p>
<ul>
              <li><a href="NSBActivities/majoractions.jsp">Major Actions &amp; Approvals</a></li> 
                <li><a href="NSBActivities/testimony.jsp">Testimony</a></li>
                <li><a href="NSBActivities/reso_state.jsp">Resolutions and Statements</a></li>
                <li><a href="NSBActivities/skilled-technical-workforce.jsp">Skilled Technical Workforce Resources</a></li>
				<li><a href="NSBActivities/merit-review-commission.jsp">Merit Review Reexamination Commission</a></li>
 <li><a href="/nsb/NSBActivities/vision-2030.jsp">Vision 2030 Resources</a></li>
												<li><a href="/nsb/NSBActivities/semiannual_report.jsp">OIG Semiannual Reports</a></li>
                <li><a href="/nsb/about/multimediagallery.jsp">Multimedia Gallery</a></li>
                
                </ul>
               
               </div>
              </div>
             </div>
            </div>
