        <div class="caption">
          <h3 align="center"><a href="https://ncses.nsf.gov/indicators">Science &amp; Engineering Indicators</a></h3>
                <p>NSB&rsquo;s  biennial report, <strong><em>Science and Engineering Indicators (Indicators)</em></strong>,  provides comprehensive, policy-neutral information on the nation’s S&amp;E enterprise.  In addition to the main report, the NSB produces a suite of <a href="/nsb/sei/index.jsp">related resources</a>.</p>
<ul>
          
			<li><a href="https://ncses.nsf.gov/indicators"><em>Science &amp; Engineering Indicators 2024</em></a></li>
